 當你同個女仔做愛 當女仔高潮時 男人都射 就代表你地兩個夾得埋 Suki清潔完之後竟然同我講：「老公仔 我地一個禮拜最小要搞兩日架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n我當然立即狗衝應承啦 估唔到係一個更加美好既開始。。。"},{"pid":"42e308957dff4a092fb78fbb7a4b87f4e8cf90fd","tid":29933,"uid":44162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/jh7e630y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjh7e630y&h=a8bd39f1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對唔住 呢排較忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ea37d3b4b5c1a39131e21659f13af02add3212","tid":29933,"uid":44162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"邊個hihi比負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c323c8b19c61091c08002806a58b049a342a87ca","tid":29933,"uid":59136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:31:27.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"070761b6f0d2547d5a4db2c50cfcd6bb6f9e9d9c","tid":29933,"uid":44162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"遲下會出整合post 方便大家收睇"},{"pid":"7ccfb0b3526509d90bf8e9d3bfbc28dc76b66667","tid":29933,"uid":44162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"今晚返到屋企會將頭五章整合 勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132ad6e22321fe46aa91ab15f05dbcf63bcc68c4","tid":29933,"uid":62099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"106654fd2120b916f79ddc9e5627362a817c7be9","tid":29933,"uid":44162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<br 